FipsState.name: FipsState
FipsState.description: The state of FIPS (140-2) encryption (disabled, crypto, or full).

BuildType.name: BuildType
BuildType.description: The type of build installed and running (production, or development).

tptNgfwSystemBuildType.name: tptNgfwSystemBuildType
tptNgfwSystemBuildType.description: The software build type (production, or development). If a development build, the revision object is populated with the source code revision otherwise it's not provided.

tptNgfwSystemBuildRevision.name: tptNgfwSystemBuildRevision
tptNgfwSystemBuildRevision.description: The software build revision. This object reports the source code revision of the development build that's installed and running. This object is empty if a production build is installed.

tptNgfwSystemBootTime.name: tptNgfwSystemBootTime
tptNgfwSystemBootTime.description: The local date and time when the device was powered on.

tptNgfwSystemUpTime.name: tptNgfwSystemUpTime
tptNgfwSystemUpTime.description: The time (in 100th/second) since the system was powered on.

tptNgfwSystemSmsManaged.name: tptNgfwSystemSmsManaged
tptNgfwSystemSmsManaged.description: Indicates if this device is under SMS management control. This object is set to true when the device is under SMS control, false otherwise.

tptNgfwSystemSmsIpAddress.name: tptNgfwSystemSmsIpAddress
tptNgfwSystemSmsIpAddress.description: The SMS IP address that is managing this device. Only set if SMS is managing the device.

tptNgfwSystemFipsAdminState.name: tptNgfwSystemFipsAdminState
tptNgfwSystemFipsAdminState.description: The administrative state of FIPS (140-2) encryption (disabled, crypto, or full)

tptNgfwSystemFipsOperState.name: tptNgfwSystemFipsOperState
tptNgfwSystemFipsOperState.description: The operational state of FIPS (140-2) encryption (disabled, crypto, or full.)

tptNgfwSystemMasterKeySet.name: tptNgfwSystemMasterKeySet
tptNgfwSystemMasterKeySet.description: Indicates if a master key (or password) has been set for the device. The value is true when a master key is set (configured), false otherwise.

tptNgfwSystemReadyNotify.name: tptNgfwSystemReadyNotify
tptNgfwSystemReadyNotify.description: A notification that the system has achieved the system ready state.

tptNgfwSystemShutdownNotify.name: tptNgfwSystemShutdownNotify
tptNgfwSystemShutdownNotify.description: A notification that the system is performing a controlled shutdown or reboot.

tptNgfwSystemSmsNotAuthNotify.name: tptNgfwSystemSmsNotAuthNotify
tptNgfwSystemSmsNotAuthNotify.description: A notification that a management station was denied control of the system because it did not have an authorized IP address. Notification includes the IP address of the management station that attempted control.

tptNgfwSystemInfoGroup.name: tptNgfwSystemInfoGroup
tptNgfwSystemInfoGroup.description: System group for Next-generation Firewall products consisting of hardware and software version information.

tptNgfwSystemNotificationGroup.name: tptNgfwSystemNotificationGroup
tptNgfwSystemNotificationGroup.description: A group of notifications related to NGFW system status.

tptNgfwSystemInfoCompl.name: tptNgfwSystemInfoCompl
tptNgfwSystemInfoCompl.description: Compliance for TippingPoint Next-generation Firewall products.
